  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2009-04-02",
    "date": "2009-06-23T22:13:47Z",
    "text": "Directs the President to modify and update the recovery.gov website to: (1) ensure that states, cities, and other general purpose political subdivisions of a state can easily ascertain whether such entity is eligible for any funds under the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act, any application deadlines that are applicable to the receipt of such funds, and the contact information of any entity responsible for the distribution of such funds; and (2) create an online database that catalogues all programs and activities under the Act."
